{"tid":1558310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"銅鑼灣A出口","createTime":"2019-09-10T11:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:51:13.000Z","uid":118158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51ccd4ff4ef50adacf224bdd89784bc43fbaad0c","tid":1558310,"uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47a363681dda81d33586a87a68839cf8f5c9c5e","tid":1558310,"uid":315793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"民陣：正申請 9.15 大遊行】<br />\n<br />\n社會及政治組織從業員工會晚上7時半在遮打花園舉行「反濫捕、抗威權集會」。民陣召集人岑子杰宣布，民陣正申請 9 月 15 日（周日）遊行，呼籲之前出過嚟的人再次上街。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪要再晒冷，嚟個百萬人奇蹟啊？<br />\n冇人提、冇人宣傳，一萬人都偷笑啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">星期日要人！<br />\n星期日要人！<br />\n星期日要人啊！！！</span>"},{"pid":"df238f2ae18e41d69ecd556e0243413a2b050c10","tid":1558310,"uid":89787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51ccd4ff4ef50adacf224bdd89784bc43fbaad0c","tid":1558310,"uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ekvEAJG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FekvEAJG.png&h=bc938735&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ce253bddc7b4c4549f7692c0a303ac66f652e48","tid":1558310,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}